	<h3>Concept</h3>
	<p>Upon choosing a concept to be prototyped with foam, the initial step involved mind mapping to determine if the artifact would be practical, artistic, a replica or representative of the material's inherit properties.<sup>1</sup> Inspired by the buoyancy of foam and prior work designing a <a href="http://vimeo.com/11462990">museum exhibit</a> showcasing 17th Century navigational sailing techniques, a characterized pirate boat seemed enjoyable and thematically appropriate. Upon referencing online imagery and scale models featured at local retailers, a series of sketches guided the prototype design.<sup>2</sup></p> 
